ZFMK 57435, female, from Ankeniheny, Alaotra-Mangoro Region, Eastern Madagascar, collected on 19 February 1994 by F. Glaw, N. Rabibisoa and O. Ramilison. This female specimen with tibial gland (
Vences et al. 2002
) is not included in the paratype series because no genetic data are available, neither for the specimen nor for the general locality Ankeniheny.
